posts.question: You've probably seen me on your Instagram (heyabsolem). I like your work cuz I feel like it's got a bit of dark humor in it smth like sarcasm. maybe it wasn't intentional, I'll never know. Anyways I'd say you're one of my favorite photographers and I really hope you don't stop doing this because it's the cause of an instant spark in people. a spark of whatever. jaw dropping. (don't yell at me I didn't ask you anything)  -Noushin
posts.answer:
Hi Noushin,

I’m not intentional about what I do, but I am conscious of it. Hope that makes sense. Thanks!
